prefix-set.rpl-prefix-set:

as-path-set.rplas-path-set:
as-path-set B2B-SPECIAL-BOGON_ASNS
  ios-regex '_0_',
  ios-regex '_(23456|65535|4294967295)_',
  passes-through '[64496..64511]',
  passes-through '[65536..65551]',
  passes-through '[64512..65221]',
  passes-through '[65223..65534]',
  passes-through '[4200000000..4294967294]',
  passes-through '[65552..131071]'
end-set

as-path-set AS_B2B_CI_CPE_BOGON_ASNS

  ios-regex '_(23456|65535|4294967295)_',

  passes-through '[64512..65221]',
  passes-through '[65223..65534]',
  passes-through '[4200000000..4294967294]',
  passes-through '[65552..131071]'

route-policy SET-TEST-IN

end-policy

route-policy RP_B2B_CI_CPE_CUSTOMER_OWN_PFX_ANTIDDOS_V6

    done
  endif
end-policy

route-policy B2B-PA-V6-ADDRESSES

    set community BLACKHOLE-LOCAL
    set community NO-EXPORT additive
    set local-preference 1000
    set next-hop 192.0.2.1
    done
  elseif (destination in PXL_B2B_CUST_VFZ_V6_Vlan* or destination in PXL_NL_MICRO6 or destination in PXL_NL_MICRO6_AS9143) then
    set community AORTAINT additive
    set local-preference 500

    done
  endif
end-policy

route-policy B2B_Special_BOGON-V4-out

    drop
  elseif as-path in B2B-SPECIAL-BOGON_ASNS then
    drop
  endif
end-policy

route-policy RP_B2B_BGP_FILTER_IN

    pass

end-policy

end-policy

route-policy B2B_COMMUNITY_BASED_ACCEPT

    set community BLACKHOLE-LOCAL
    set community NO-EXPORT additive
    set local-preference 1000
    set next-hop 192.0.2.1
    done

    set local-preference 1000
    set next-hop 192.0.2.1

  elseif community matches-any CUSTTRANS then

    drop
